jab Abu Muslim ko ailaaniya daawat aur taqat ke istemal ki ijazat mili hai to ye wo zamana tha ke kharaasan mein karami aur nusra bin sayair ki ladaiyon ka silsila jaari tha, jaisa ke oopar bayan ho chuka hai, abu muslim ne apni jamaat ke logon ko faham kiya aur un koale ckrmani aur nusra bin sayair ke darmiyaan mein kheema zan hua aur bilaakhir kharaani qatal hua, is ka ladka Ali Bin Karmani Abu Muslim ke pas a gaya aur abu muslim ne nus ko meero se khaarij karke marapur qabza kar liya; magarchand roza qayam ke baad marawwi se mahawan ki jaanib chala aaya, nus bin sayair ne Marwan Bin Muhammad Khalifia Delhi ko aamadaad ke liye khat likha tha, Marwan Bin Muhammad in dinon zikh bin qais kharji se masroofe jang tha, wo koi madad nus ke pas nahi bhej sakda jin aam mein nus kee arz radd Marwan ke pas pahunchi unhein dinon imam ibraheem ka khat jo muslim ke naam unhon ne rawaan kiya tha aur jis mein likha tha ke kharaasan mein arabi zabaan bolne walon ko zindah na chhodne aur nusra karnri donon ka khatma kardeena, pakda gaya aur Marwanul Jama'a ki khidmat mein pesh hua; yahi pehla mauqa tha ke bunewamiya ko abbasiyon ki saazi sha ka haalu maloom hua, Marwan ne ilaqe Belqa ke aamil kolka ke imam ibraheem ko hameema mein jakar giraftar karlo; chunancha imam ibraheem giraftaar hokar aaye aur Marwan ne un ko qaid kar diya, jaisa ke oopar zikr aachka hai, abu muslim ne kharaasan mein jab ailaaniya daawat wa tableegh shuroo ki tokharaasan ke log jok darjauq is ke pas aane lage.
